title: To my future self...
author: Victor Gutierrez
content:
Keep Hustling

Keep hustling. Keep working. Keep studying.
When doubts come, that’s proof you’re on the right path.
Because growth hurts. Evolution is uncomfortable.

Keep hustling. Keep studying. Keep giving your best.
Results will come. Pressure is just noise.

Just keep going.
